1. *Krv* mu je potekla iz nosa. (His blood was running out of his nose.)
2. Ona je nosila *krvavu* haljinu. (She was wearing a bloody dress.)
3. Ona je *krvarila*. (She was bleeding.)
4. Oni su se borili do *krvi*. (They were fighting until blood was shed.)
5. *Krvav* trag je dokaz da je on tu bio. (The bloody trace is a proof that he was here.)
6. On se *krvlju* zakleo da će to učiniti. (He swore in blood that he would do it.)